Author: mknzngcnb
Text: I’m not too worried about the whole insurance thing, I’m from Canada and I’m status First Nation so I should be good for finding the help I need.   Good luck on your treatment journey!

Author: SubBiscuit
Text: I'm super proud of you! I recently started the "try to find treatment" journey as well. It can be tough and the insurance might deny your first request, but they'll normally accept after an appeal. For OP they likely won't deny though, that's for higher levels of care.  We are all behind you and doing what you want for yourself!
